thread.title: BRIEF-Ups To Purchase 14 Additional 747-8F Freighters, Orders 4 New 767S

title: BRIEF-Ups To Purchase 14 Additional 747-8F Freighters, Orders 4 New 767S
text:
February 1, 2018 / 3:15 PM / in 6 minutes BRIEF-Ups To Purchase 14 Additional 747-8F Freighters, Orders 4 New 767S Reuters Staff 
Feb 1 (Reuters) - United Parcel Service Inc: 
* UPS COMMITS TO PURCHASE 14 ADDITIONAL 747-8F FREIGHTERS AND ORDERS 4 NEW 767S 
* UPS - ALL OF NEW AIRCRAFT WILL BE ADDED TO EXISTING FLEET AND NO EXISTING AIRCRAFT ARE BEING REPLACED * UPS - ALL 32 OF JETS WILL BE DELIVERED BY END OF 2022 
* UPS - ‍AIRCRAFT WILL BE DELIVERED ON AN EXPEDITED SCHEDULE, BUILDING ON CO‘S 2016 ORDER OF 14 BOEING 747-8 FREIGHTERS​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
